{"tid":1686892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［和你砌圖］將靚靚文宣變成你嘅珍藏","createTime":"2019-11-01T12:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T02:50:52.000Z","uid":58255,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"681fd552d4a153b7a7c4f0897544f77c4c56a52e","tid":1686892,"uid":58255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"（代po)<br />\n<br />\n大家行過連儂牆一定會經常比啲靚文宣吸引到<br />\n手足嘅創意同功力真係勁到世界級<br />\n正所謂文宣很清楚開花這個責任<br />\n你地嘅每一幅創作都打動人心！多謝你地！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5XV9u2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5XV9u2.jpg&h=78b16e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n作為一個砌圖L，當然想將呢啲藝術品造成砌圖掛喺屋企<br />\n日日提醒自己光復香港時代革命<br />\n但訂嘅時候都遇到阻滯<br />\n所以都想將我嘅經驗分享比同好<br />\n<br />\n其實我一開始喺香港舖頭問過<br />\n老闆話佢都好想幫我<br />\n但因為間廠喺個玻璃心國家<br />\n所以佢都有心無力<br />\n<br />\n咁冇計啦 唯有上google搵外國勢力幫手<br />\n雖然都搵到一啲外國訂砌圖網站<br />\n但有啲個廠其實都喺強国<br />\n所以真係要睇清楚公司資料<br />\n有啲網站未必會寫明佢地個廠喺邊<br />\n搏唔搏得過就你自己決定啦<br />\n咁我費事又比人cut單 所以就不了<br />\n<br />\n我最終搵到一間個廠喺歐盟嘅公司<br />\n訂咗幅1000塊嘅兄弟爬山砌圖<br />\n間公司係可以直接國際速遞嚟香港嘅<br />\n不過我就揀咗唔直接送過嚟 兜咗少少路<br />\n<br />\n開箱時係有一個快遞膠袋包住<br />\n仲有一個紙盒先會見到盒砌圖<br />\n所以基本上冇人知你訂咗咩樣嘅砌圖<br />\n唔怕扣關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAsnPvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAsnPvb.jpg&h=c2314501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3pdWac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3pdWac.jpg&h=22b82450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢嚟講，因為我只訂一幅所以貴啲<br />\nEURO 37.99 (未計shipping)<br />\n建議大家夾多幾個朋友一齊<br />\n咁單價會平啲 同埋可以share shipping<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOJm43D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOJm43D.jpg&h=111d2aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n砌圖本身品質唔錯，令面嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMu143J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMu143J.jpg&h=c2a8a0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然你要用好高解象度嘅原圖去印啦<br />\n所以記住問咗創作者先<br />\n就算open source都要尊重返人地<br />\n唔係比你商業用途拎去賣<br />\n唔好食人血饅頭呀<br />\n<br />\n利申：所用之文宣圖已得作者harcourtromanticist同意分享<br />\n<br />\n好期待砌好、上膠水、上框、上牆嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 香港人同拼圖一樣都係缺一不可<br />\n各位 聽日見啦 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5affa48f127fdcda1cc5387271e8b5211d34a54f","tid":1686892,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:25:28.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署 】依個就快截止⚠️<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=ec3e8f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=ca53fef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n簽&gt;記得email確認&gt;傳開去"},{"pid":"6106ffbfbaab2ca91a7e7f05da3cb0715db2fc71","tid":1686892,"uid":23333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"有無完成品圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598790cb08a6cc025cb6f5082714ee78f2803963","tid":1686892,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" c