,"uid":58255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61c01f1d4e868c8bfe72f6f3a286dcff13a36af2","tid":1686892,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"正喎 唔知最大可以砌幾多塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"間廠最大可造2000塊，但要視乎個圖檔解像度夠唔夠。upload咗個file，揀咗造幾大，個網站就可以話你知圖像質素高唔高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820605e69f9ac06f7d2a6df4c1442527c86b5d7b","tid":1686892,"uid":90945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"想知完成左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日612呢排又睇緊砌圖既野...<br />\n想睇下如果完成品靚...<br />\n可能跟機"}]}